- Logo proportions and alignment based on golden ratio
- Ensures mathematical precision and visual harmony

### Saving Culture
- All designs should instill the culture of saving
- Common brand objective across all communications

### Versatility
- Adaptable color palette for different audiences
- Corporate vs. consumer communication flexibility

